#. Tag: title
#: browsing.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing"
msgstr "Pretraživanje"

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:11
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Once you have annotated your images and videos, &kphotoalbum; is ready to "
#| "let you browse through your images, see <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-with-"
#| "images\"/>. If you compare that to <xref linkend=\"fig-empty-browser-"
#| "window\"/> , you will see that there now is items available in each of "
#| "the categories for <literal>People</literal>, <literal>Places</literal>, "
#| "and <literal>Keywords</literal>."
msgid ""
"Once you have annotated your images and videos, &kphotoalbum; is ready to "
"let you browse through your images. If you compare that to <xref linkend="
"\"fig-empty-browser-window\"/> , you will see that there now is items "
"available in each of the categories for <literal>People</literal>, "
"<literal>Places</literal>, and <literal>Keywords</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Nakon što ste pribilježili slike i video snimke,&kphotoalbum; je spreman za "
"pregledanje vaših slika, pogledajte <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-with-images"
"\"/>. Ako uporedite sa <xref linkend = \"fig-empty-browser-window\"/>, "
"vidjet ćete da sada postoji dostupnost stavki u svakoj od kategorija za "
"<literal> Ljudi </literal>, <literal>Mjesta</literal>,i<literal> Ključne "
"riječi</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:17
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the browser window you can see the categories you typed information into "
"when annotating your images and videos. In addition there are items for "
"searching based on EXIF information on images, browsing the folder structure "
"of your hard disk, and of course showing the actual thumbnails. Lets "
"describe each item in turn."
msgstr ""
"U prozoru preglednika možete vidjeti kategorije u koje ste upisali podatke "
"kada bilježite svoje slike i video zapise. Pored toga postoje stavke za "
"pretraživanje na osnovu EXIF informacije o slikama, pretražujete strukturu "
"foldera hard diska, i naravno pokazuje stvarne sličice. Hajdemo opisati "
"svaku stavku po redu."

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:23
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing the mouse on <literal>People</literal>, the browser window will "
"change, as you can see in <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-for-persons\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Pritiskom miša na <literal>Ljudi</literal>, prozor preglednika će se "
"promijeniti, kao što možete vidjeti u <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-for-persons"
"\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: browsing.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browser window when People was selected."
msgstr "Prozor Preglednika kada je izabran Ljudi."

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:37
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "The browser is now populated with the people you specified for your "
#| "images and videos <footnote><para>You may notice that the item "
#| "<literal>Pets</literal> has a special icon. For details about that, see "
#| "<xref linkend=\"sec-specifying-categories\"/>.</para></footnote>, "
#| "selecting a person will bring you back to the original state for the "
#| "browser, as we saw in <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-with-images\"/>, this "
#| "time, however, we are <emphasis>in the scope</emphasis> of the person we "
#| "selected. That means that we only shows information about images and "
#| "videos containing that person. See <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-for-jesper"
#| "\"/> below, which is the result of us selecting the Person "
#| "<literal>Jesper</literal>, you can see an indication of that in the "
#| "bottom of the window. Please compare <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-with-"
#| "images\"/> with <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-for-jesper\"/>, where you "
#| "will see that the number of available images and videos has gone down "
#| "from 25 to 12, and the amount of items for the different categories have "
#| "also changed."
msgid ""
"The browser is now populated with the people you specified for your images "
"and videos <footnote><para>You may notice that the item <literal>Pets</"
"literal> has a special icon. For details about that, see <xref linkend=\"sec-"
"specifying-categories\"/>.</para></footnote>, selecting a person will bring "
"you back to the original state for the browser. This time, however, we are "
"<emphasis>in the scope</emphasis> of the person we selected. That means that "
"we only show information about images and videos containing that person. See "
"<xref linkend=\"fig-browser-for-jesper\"/> below, which is the result of us "
"selecting the Person <literal>Jesper</literal>, you can see an indication of "
"that in the bottom of the window. On the lower right side of <xref linkend="
"\"fig-browser-for-jesper\"/>, you will see that the number of matching "
"images and videos has gone down from 25 to 13, while the total number of "
"images stayed the same."
msgstr ""
"Pretraživač je sada popunjen s ljudima koje ste odredili za svoje slike i "
"video zapise <footnote> <para> Možete zapaziti da je stavka "
"<literal>Ljubimci</literal> ima posebnu ikonu. Za detalje o tome, pogledajte "
"<xref linkend=\"sec-specifying-categories\"/>.</para></footnote>, odabir "
"osoba će vas vratiti u prvobitno stanje za preglednik, kao što smo vidjeli u "
"<xref linkend=\"fig-browser-with-images\"/>, ovaj put, međutim, mi smo "
"<emphasis>u okviru </emphasis> osobe koju smo izabrali. To znači da samo "
"prikazujemo informacije o slikama i video zapise koji sadrže tu osobu. "
"Pogledajte <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-for-jesper\"/> u nastavku, što je "
"rezultat  nas odabirom Osoba <literal>Jesper</literal>, možete vidjeti "
"naznaku da je u dnu prozora. Molimo vas da usporedite <xref linkend=\"fig-"
"browser-with-images\"/>sa<xref linkend=\"fig-browser-for-jesper\"/>, gdje "
"ćete vidjeti da je broj raspoloživih slika i video zapisa opao od 25 na12, a "
"iznos stavki za različite kategorije su se također promijenila."

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that if there are only a few images in the scope, &kphotoalbum; will "
"directly go to the thumbnail viewer (see <xref linkend=\"chp-thumbnail-view"
"\"/>). You can configure this behaviour in the thumbnail viewer settings "
"(see <xref linkend=\"opt-thumbnails\"/>)."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: browsing.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browser limited to the scope of the person <literal>Jesper</literal>"
msgstr "Preglednik ograničen na opseg osobe <literal>Jesper</literal>"

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:65
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If we now continue selecting a new person, then we will get to the images "
"containing both people. Continuing that way you can narrow the set of images "
"that you have in mind down to a few images from a set of thousands."
msgstr ""
"Ako smo sada nastavili odabirom nove osobe, onda ćemo doći do slika koje "
"sadrže oboje ljudi. Nastavljajući taj način možete suziti skup slika koje "
"imate na umu do nekoliko slika iz skupa nekoliko hiljada."

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you are done limiting the scope of images, you may select the "
"<guilabel>View Thumbnails</guilabel> icon, to see exactly those images "
"matching your current scope."
msgstr ""
"Kada ste gotovi sa ograničavanjem obima slika, možete odabrati <guilabel> "
"Pogledaj Sličice </guilabel> ikonu, da vidite upravo one slike koje "
"zadovoljavaju vaš trenutni obim."

#. Tag: title
#: browsing.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adding Preview Images to the Browser"
msgstr "Dodavanje Prethodnih Slika na Preglednik"

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Looking at <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-for-persons\"/> you will see that "
"each person has the same icon in front of his name. &kphotoalbum; is "
"actually capable of showing a preview image for each individual person "
"<footnote><para>This of course also applies to places, keywords, and other "
"categories you have defined yourself.</para></footnote> as can be seen in "
"<xref linkend=\"fig-imagesForPersons\"/>."
msgstr ""
"Gledajući <xref linkend=\"fig-browser-for-persons\"/> vidjet ćete da svaka "
"osoba ima istu ikonu ispred njegovog imena. &kphotoalbum; je zapravo "
"sposoban da pokazuje prethodno prikazanu sliku za svaku pojedinačnu osobu "
"<footnote> <para> To se naravno odnosi i na mjesta, ključne riječi i ostale "
"kategorije koje ste sami definisali.</para> </footnote> kao što se može "
"vidjeti u <xref linkend=\"fig-imagesForPersons\"/>."

#. Tag: title
#: browsing.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Images for each Individual Person"
msgstr "Slike za svaku Pojedinačnu Osobu"

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To show images along with the names, choose the tool button to the very "
"right of the toolbar, that will bring up a popup menu, where you can chose "
"which view you want to use for the given category. Notice views must be "
"configured for each category - that way you may for example use an icon view "
"for people, but a plain list view for keywords (in case you can't come up "
"with good images for your keywords)."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz slike zajedno s imenima, odabrati dugme alata do samog  na alatnoj "
"traci, koji će prikazati iskakujući meni, gdje možete odabrati koji prikaz "
"želite da koristite za datu kategoriju. Obaviještavajući prikazi moraju biti "
"konfigurirani za svaku kategoriju - na taj način možete na primjer koristiti "
"ikonu za ljude, ali običan prikaz liste za ključne riječi (u slučaju da ne "
"možete doći do dobrih slika za vaše ključne riječi)."

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is, however, your job to tell it which images to use for each individual "
"person. To do so, you must open the viewer (see <xref linkend=\"chp-viewer\"/"
">), and from the context menu choose <guimenuitem>Show Category Editor</"
"guimenuitem>, this will bring up the category editor which can be seen in "
"<xref linkend=\"fig-categoryEditor\"/>. In the category editor you choose "
"the image for the given person. In the viewer it is possible to zoom to part "
"of the image, and that way crop what part should be shown."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je, međutim, vaš posao da kažete koja od slika će se koristiti za svaku "
"pojedinačnu osobu. Da biste to učinili, morate otvoriti preglednik (vidi "
"<xref linkend=\"CHP-Viewer\"/>), i iz kontekstnog menija odaberite "
"<guimenuitem>Prikaži Kategoriju Urednika</guimenuitem>, to će dovesti do "
"urednika kategorije, koji se može vidjeti u <xref linkend=\"fig-"
"categoryEditor\"/>. U urednik kategoriji odaberite sliku za datu osobu. U "
"pregledniku moguće je zumirati na dio slike, i na taj način podrezati dio "
"koji treba biti prikazan."

#. Tag: title
#: browsing.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Category Editor"
msgstr "Kategorija Urednika"

#. Tag: title
#: browsing.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "General image searches"
msgstr "Opšte pretrage slike"

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you chose the <guilabel>Search</guilabel> item in the browser, you will "
"get to a dialog with great resemblance to the dialog you used for setting "
"properties of your images. You can see this dialog in <xref linkend=\"fig-"
"search\"/> below."
msgstr ""
"Ako ste odabrali <guilabel>Pretraga</guilabel> stavku u pretraživaču, dobit "
"ćete dijalog sa velikom sličnošću na dijalog koji ste koristili za "
"postavljanje svojstva vaših slika. Možete vidjeti ovaj dijalog u <xref "
"linkend=\"fig-search\"/> ispod."

#. Tag: title
#: browsing.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search dialog"
msgstr "Dijalog pretrage"

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you type a string in the label or description field, then that text will "
"be searched for using substring searches. Likewise you can also specify a "
"date to search for, either as part of a date, say 1971, or as a complete "
"date. You may also specify date ranges, like 1971-1980."
msgstr ""
"Ako upišete string na etiketi ili opisnom polju, onda taj tekst će se "
"tražiti pomoću podniza pretrage. Isto tako možete odrediti datum za "
"traženje, bilo kao dio datuma, recimo 1971. godine, ili kao kompletan datum. "
"Možete također odrediti datum koji se kreće,  od 1971-1980."

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The options item allows a very limited form of writing an expression, as you "
"can see in the example in <xref linkend=\"fig-search\"/>. Here we search for "
"images with <literal>Jesper</literal>, but without <literal>Anne Helene</"
"literal>."
msgstr ""
"Stavka opcija omogućava vrlo ograničen oblik pisanja izraza, kao što možete "
"vidjeti na primjeru u <xref linkend=\"fig-search\"/>. Ovdje ćemo tražiti "
"slike sa <literal>Jesper</literal>, ali bez <literal>Anne Helene</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: browsing.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The allowed operations are &amp; (meaning: and), | (meaning: or), and ! "
"(meaning: not)."
msgstr ""
"Dozvoljene operacije su &amp; meaningi: and), | (meaningi: or), and ! "
"(meaning: not)."

#~ msgid "Browser when images and videos have been annotated"
#~ msgstr "Pregledavanje kada su slike i video zapisi pribilježeni"
